{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/groups-and-permissions.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>You can have customized groups with different access rights on your program. HackerOne program administrators can set these access rights for groups on your team. All security programs start with Admin and Standard default groups with set permissions that you can't edit, but you can still add or remove users to these groups.</p>\n<h3 id=\"adding-a-new-group\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-a-new-group\" aria-label=\"adding a new group permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding a New Group</h3>\n<p>To add a new group and set access rights:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to your program's <strong>Program Settings > General > Group Management</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Add Group</strong>.</li>\n<li>Write the name of the group in the <strong>Name</strong> field.</li>\n<li>Select the permissions you want to enable for the group. You can select from these options:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Report</td>\n<td>Users in the group can: <ul><li>Post comments</li><li>Change report states</li><li>Edit report titles and vulnerability types</li><li>Suggest bounties</li><li>Add/Remove external participants from reports</li><li>Edit common responses</li><li>Edit triggers</li><li>Request public disclosure</li><li>Agree to public disclosure request</li><li>Create CVE ID Requests</li><li>Transfer reports</li></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Program</td>\n<td>Users in the group can: <ul><li>Edit profile, program and bounty settings</li><li>Invite hackers</li><li>View billing information</li><li>Edit inbox views</li></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Reward</td>\n<td>Users in the group can: <ul><li>Grant rewards</li><li>Post comments</li><li>Suggest bounties</li></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Admin</td>\n<td>Users in the group can: <ul><li>Add/Remove users</li><li>Edit user permissions</li></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<blockquote>\n<p><i>Note: All groups have the ability to view reports and post internal comments by default.</i></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Click <strong>Create</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"user group\"\n        title=\"user group\"\n        src=\"/static/52f5a08ac04fab45927f908129c7fac0/0b533/user-group.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52f5a08ac04fab45927f908129c7fac0/fac75/user-group.png 125w,\n/static/52f5a08ac04fab45927f908129c7fac0/63868/user-group.png 250w,\n/static/52f5a08ac04fab45927f908129c7fac0/0b533/user-group.png 500w,\n/static/52f5a08ac04fab45927f908129c7fac0/1d69c/user-group.png 750w,\n/static/52f5a08ac04fab45927f908129c7fac0/0fb99/user-group.png 965w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>To edit your group name and permissions, click <strong>Edit</strong> next to the group you want to edit in <strong>Settings > General > Group Management</strong>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"adding-or-removing-users\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-or-removing-users\" aria-label=\"adding or removing users permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding or Removing Users</h3>\n<p>To add or remove users:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Click <strong>Add/Remove users</strong>.</li>\n<li>Select the checkbox of the users you want to add to the group.</li>\n<li>Deselect the checkboxes of the users you want to remove from the group.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Update</strong>.  </li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"tutorial-video\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tutorial-video\" aria-label=\"tutorial video permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tutorial Video</h3>\n<iframe id=\"ytplayer\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/4yQnKcBWIjI?rel=0&autoplay=0&origin={{Â site.url }}\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/groups-and-permissions.html","id":"programs/groups-and-permissions","title":"Groups and Permissions","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Adding a New Group"},{"value":"Adding or Removing Users"},{"value":"Tutorial Video"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}